snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Video Song | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil presents the video song of ‚ÄúThangapoovey‚Äù from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh‚Äôs music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film‚Äôs emotional landscape.

snippet.title: The Chase Teaser: R Madhavan & MS Dhoni Together | Mahi in Action Avatar | Vasan Bala
snippet.description:
The Chase Teaser: R Madhavan & MS Dhoni Together | Mahi in Action Avatar | Vasan Bala


Friends the wait is finally over! On 7th September, R. Madhavan dropped a massive surprise on social media ‚Äì the official teaser of ‚ÄúThe Chase‚Äù directed by Vasan Bala. But the real shocker? Legendary cricketer MS Dhoni joins Madhavan as a Task Force Officer! Both Madhavan and Dhoni are seen in uniform, bringing raw action and power-packed energy on screen. The teaser has already gone viral on Instagram and fans can‚Äôt stop saying ‚Äì ‚ÄúMaddy and Mahi together = Fire!‚Äù Dhoni, who has earlier appeared in ads and even a cameo in Tamil movie ‚ÄúGOAT,‚Äù is now seen in a completely new avatar that has left fans speechless. Meanwhile, Madhavan continues to surprise audiences with versatile roles, and this time he looks deadlier than ever!

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively.

Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: The Chase teaser, #Madhavan and #Dhoni stepping into character as officers on a high-stakes mission
snippet.description:
MS Dhoni has done just about everything on a cricket field, masterminded chases, stayed cool under fire, and even walked away with three ICC trophies. But now, the former India skipper has turned heads for something very different: wielding guns in an action-packed teaser alongside Bollywood star R Madhavan.

What came as a big surprise on August 7, Madhavan surprised fans by dropping the clip of his upcoming project The Chase, directed by Vasan Bala. The teaser shows both Madhavan and Dhoni dressed in tactical black gear, complete with bulletproof vests and sunglasses, stepping into character as officers on a high-stakes mission. The sight of ‚ÄúCaptain Cool‚Äù in an action sequence sent social media into overdrive, with fans already dubbing it Dhoni‚Äôs big-screen debut.

bhoola woh zindagi jo thi 
bin tere 

Tera hi zikr goonjta 
meri yeh dhadkanon ki 
vaadi mein 

Tu woh mehak alaav ki 
jo door se bhi sekti 
mera dil yeh 

Kaafi hai bas Tera Hona

snippet.title: Ram Jaane (Music Video) Anu Malik | Shahrukh Khan, Juhi Chawla | Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam|Hindi song
snippet.description:
‚ÄúRam Jaane‚Äù is the bold and unforgettable title track from the 1995 Bollywood action-drama Ram Jaane, sung by Udit Narayan, Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam and composed by Anu Malik. The song captures the gritty, rebellious spirit of the film‚Äôs lead character, played by Shah Rukh Khan, whose very name ‚Äî Ram Jaane (meaning ‚ÄúGod knows‚Äù) ‚Äî becomes a powerful identity statement.

#RamJaane #ShahRukhKhan #JuhiChawla #UditNarayan #AlkaYagnik #SonuNigam #AnuMalik #BollywoodClassics #SRKMovies #BollywoodAction #HindiMovieSongs #RamJaaneSong #BollywoodHits #EvergreenBollywood #SRKFans #BollywoodSoundtrack #ClassicSRK #IndianCinema #BollywoodAnthems #BollywoodThrowback #DesiVibes 

Credits: 
Singer: Udit Narayan, Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam
Music: Anu Malik
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Ram Jaane
Starring: Shahrukh Khan, Juhi Chawla
Director: Rajiv Mehra
Producer: Parvesh Mehra
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics:

Kehthe hain log muje "ram jaane"
Kaise padaa ye mera naam jaane
Kaise padaa ye mera naam jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
O, ram jaane, ye to bataa
Tere sa dil ka raaja bana
Paise ka kaise ghulaam jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
‚ô™
Yaaron, mazaa lene do zaraa sa
Barson raha hoon main bhookha-pyaasaa
Vo ik haqiqat hai, o, deewaane
Samajh hai tune jiskoo tamaasha
‚ô™
Mat chhed mujko, aa hosh mein
Paagal javanee ke josh mein
Mat chhed mujko, aa hosh mein
Paagal javanee ke josh mein
Too pee gaya kithne jam jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
‚ô™
Jo jhooth-sach ko pahachaanata hai
Duniyaa mein jeenaa vo jaanata hai
Hum kya karen, hum tujhse alag hain
Hum maut ko zindagi maanata hai
‚ô™
Maranaa hai ik din saba ko, magar
O, bekhabar, tujko kya khabar
Maranaa hai ik din saba ko, magar
O, bekhabar, tujko kya khabar
Kya hai tera anjaam jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
Ram jaane, ram jaane
‚ô™
Kaise tera toota dil jod doon main?
Dil chaahe saba ka dil tod doon main
Ho, nafrat naa kar, khud se pyaar kar too
Too "haan " kahe to ye zid chhod doon main
‚ô™
Ye to naseebon ka kaam hai
Har dil pe likhaa ek naam hai
